      "comment": "NO FIZZY DRINK (8) is a fast beginner but out of character last time when always well back and missed the placings, finishing fifth (23.23) in a Grade 6 at this track. Was fast away and placed (23.23) at this track the start prior. Solid record here winning two races. Has ability and can bounce back. ZIPPING THERON (2) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at this track over 531m behind Agent Twenty One (31.57) in a Grade 6. Placed at her previous run. Bold showing expected. BIG BOSS GIBLET (6) claimed an on-pace win two back then gave a start but got home into the frame when second at this track (30.95). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to feature again. YOU SEE ME (1) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
